/docs/merchant-continuity-and-critical-incidents.md:198:| December | Summarize incident themes | Year-end review |
/docs/merchant-continuity-and-critical-incidents.md:204:When this document conflicts with a dedicated policy, the dedicated policy wins. When this document sounds urgent but the customer request depends on identity, basket ownership, payment state, discount authority, return state, package evidence, financing eligibility, or risk review, do not treat continuity language as approval.
